query:
SELECT d.id, d.name, d.fileUrl, d.mimeType, d.fileKey, h.name as hotelName
FROM documents d
JOIN hotels h ON d.hotelId = h.id
WHERE h.name LIKE '%Vienna%Parking%'
LIMIT 5;
